<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Business Proposal</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .cover {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .cover .company-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .cover .doc-title {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111827;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .cover .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .cover .meta {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .cover .meta strong {
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .prepared-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        .prepared-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .prepared-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .prepared-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .prepared-detail {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .highlight-box p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #1e40af;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .deliverables-list {
            padding-left: 0;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .deliverables-list li {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .deliverables-list li::before {
            content: "✓";
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #ecfdf5;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: 700;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .pricing-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .pricing-table thead th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .pricing-table thead th:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .pricing-table tbody td {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .pricing-table tbody td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .total-box {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .total-display {
            background: #111827;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .total-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .total-value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .timeline-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .timeline-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            padding: 12px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .timeline-phase {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .timeline-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .timeline-duration {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: #111827;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .cta-text {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .cta-sub {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .terms-section {
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .terms-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .sig-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .sig-field {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .sig-field-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sig-field-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="cover">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="doc-title">{{#if proposalTitle}}{{proposalTitle}}{{else}}Business Proposal{{/if}}</div>
        <div class="doc-subtitle">{{#if proposalSubtitle}}{{proposalSubtitle}}{{else}}A comprehensive proposal for your
            consideration{{/if}}</div>
        <div class="meta"><strong>Date:</strong> {{proposalDate}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Proposal No:</strong> {{#if
            proposalNumber}}{{proposalNumber}}{{else}}BP-2024-001{{/if}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="prepared-grid">
        <div class="prepared-card">
            <div class="prepared-label">Prepared By</div>
            <div class="prepared-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="prepared-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if companyEmail}}<div class="prepared-detail">{{companyEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="prepared-card">
            <div class="prepared-label">Prepared For</div>
            <div class="prepared-name">{{clientName}}</div>
            <div class="prepared-detail">{{{clientAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if clientEmail}}<div class="prepared-detail">{{clientEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Executive Summary</div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p>{{{executiveSummary}}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Scope of Work</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>{{{scopeOfWork}}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Deliverables</div>
        <ul class="deliverables-list">
            {{#each deliverables}}
            <li>{{this}}</li>
            {{/each}}
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Investment</div>
        <table class="pricing-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Service / Item</th>
                    <th>Amount</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each items}}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{this.description}}</td>
                    <td>₹{{this.amount}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="total-box">
            <div class="total-display">
                <div class="total-label">Total Investment</div>
                <div class="total-value">₹{{totalAmount}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Timeline</div>
        <div class="timeline-section">
            <div class="timeline-grid">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-phase">Phase 1</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Discovery & Planning</div>
                    <div class="timeline-duration">{{#if phase1Duration}}{{phase1Duration}}{{else}}Week 1-2{{/if}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-phase">Phase 2</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Development & Execution</div>
                    <div class="timeline-duration">{{#if phase2Duration}}{{phase2Duration}}{{else}}Week 3-6{{/if}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-phase">Phase 3</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Testing & Review</div>
                    <div class="timeline-duration">{{#if phase3Duration}}{{phase3Duration}}{{else}}Week 7-8{{/if}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-phase">Phase 4</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Launch & Handover</div>
                    <div class="timeline-duration">{{#if phase4Duration}}{{phase4Duration}}{{else}}Week 9-10{{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Terms & Conditions</div>
        <ol class="terms-list">
            <li>This proposal is valid for {{#if validityDays}}{{validityDays}}{{else}}30{{/if}} days from the date of
                issue.</li>
            <li>Payment terms: {{#if paymentTerms}}{{paymentTerms}}{{else}}50% on acceptance, 50% on project
                completion{{/if}}.</li>
            <li>The project scope is as defined in this proposal. Any changes will be handled through a formal change
                request process.</li>
            <li>All prices are exclusive of applicable taxes unless otherwise stated.</li>
            <li>Both parties agree to maintain confidentiality of all shared information.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-text">Ready to get started?</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">Sign below to accept this proposal and begin the engagement</div>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-card">
            <div class="sig-title">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Name & Title</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig-card">
            <div class="sig-title">Client Acceptance</div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Name: {{clientName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{companyName}} — Business Proposal</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>